PN,31301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,FA woman who was unable to see
OL,7,Ffollowing the birth of her first child
OL,8,Fhas had her sight restored following a
OL,9,Fplasma donation.
OL,11,FJessica Kent-Hazledine said she feared
OL,12,Fshe "wouldn't be able to see my baby
OL,13,Fgrow up" when her vision started to go
OL,14,Fin April last year, but a year on her
OL,15,Fsight is "so much better".
OL,17,FThe 33-year-old dentist from Cornwall
OL,18,Fwoke up two weeks after having her son
OL,19,Fwith little vision in her left eye,
OL,20,Fwhich she put down to tiredness.
OL,26,@wD@JOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
