OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,FHowever, she soon lost vision in her
OL,7,Fright eye, leaving her "terrified"
OL,8,Fthat she would not see her baby grow
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,F"I was a new mum, not getting much
OL,12,Fsleep," Ms Kent-Hazledine said.
OL,14,F"But I thought I should probably get
OL,15,Fit checked out and the next thing I
OL,16,Fknew I was having an urgent MRI and
OL,17,Fblood tests. It was all very scary, I
OL,18,Fwas thinking the worst.
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@bO]sD@AOUtD@GO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,F"When my vision went in my right eye,
OL,7,Ftoo, I was terrified ` I thought I
OL,8,Fwouldn't be able to see my baby grow
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,F"I had been a mum for two weeks and
OL,12,Fwas faced with the prospect of not
OL,13,Fbeing able to see my son again, it was
OL,14,Fawful."
OL,16,FAfter trying some other treatments,
OL,17,Fmedics arranged a plasma exchange for
OL,18,FMs Kent-Hazledine which was carried
OL,19,Fout by a new service run by NHS Blood
OL,20,Fand Transplant (NHSBT)in the South
OL,21,FWest.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
