PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,FAs part of the process, a patient's
OL,7,Fplasma - the liquid component of blood
OL,8,Fthat helps transport blood cells,
OL,9,Fnutrients and hormones around the body
OL,10,F- is removed from the bloodstream and
OL,11,Freplaced with donor plasma.
OL,13,FThis helped stop the antibodies in Ms
OL,14,FKent-Hazledine's blood from attacking
OL,15,Fand damaging the protective layer
OL,16,Faround the nerve fibres in her eyes.
OL,18,FShe can now see clearly out of her
OL,19,Fright eye and has around 75% sight in
OL,20,Fher left.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,F"It's been almost a year now and my
OL,7,Fsight is so much better - I still have
OL,8,Fsome blurring in half of my left eye
OL,9,Fbut I can look after my son and live
OL,10,Fan independent life, which I was
OL,11,Fworried I wouldn't be able to", she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe plasma exchange was performed by
OL,15,FNHSBT's therapeutic apheresis services
OL,16,F(TAS), which is working with four
OL,17,Fhospitals in the region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
