PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShe added: "I'm eternally grateful to
OL,12,Fthose people who donated blood and
OL,13,Fplasma - it's only thanks to them that
OL,14,Fthat plasma was available and I'm able
OL,15,Fto see again.
OL,17,F"I don't think people realise just how
OL,18,Fmuch good donation can do - we all
OL,19,Fknow blood can be used in emergencies
OL,20,Fbut it can also be used to help so
OL,21,Fmany people like me.
OL,26,@sD@LOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,F"I'd urge absolutely everybody who is
OL,7,Feligible to go and give blood or
OL,8,Fplasma ` and thank you to those who
OL,9,Falready do."
OL,11,FEmma Warner, lead nurse at NHS Blood
OL,12,Fand Transplant's TAS in Plymouth, who
OL,13,Ftreated Ms Kent-Hazledine, said: "This
OL,14,Fvital service is giving patients
OL,15,Faccess to timely, specialist care
OL,16,Fclose to home.
OL,18,F"For new mum Jessica, this meant
OL,19,Feverything.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]uD@bOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
