FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775139066
OL,3,CNew mother who lost sight after birth
OL,4,Chas vision restored with donated plasma
OL,6,F"She was able to receive the treatment
OL,7,Fshe needed as an outpatient, staying
OL,8,Fby her baby's side instead of enduring
OL,9,Flong, stressful journeys or the
OL,10,Fprospect of being admitted far from
OL,11,Fhome."
